# Demo Spring Boot REST API

[Back](../../README.md)

- [Demo Spring Boot REST API](#demo-spring-boot-rest-api)
  - [Single Stage](#single-stage)
  - [Multi-stages](#multi-stages)
  - [Diff](#diff)

---

## Single Stage

```sh
cd backend/springboot
docker build -t spring-api:single -f Dockerfile.single .
docker run -d --name spring-api-single -p 8080:8080 spring-api:single
```

## Multi-stages

```sh
docker build -t spring-api:multiple -f Dockerfile.multiple .
docker run -d --name spring-api-multiple -p 8080:8080 spring-api:multiple
```

## Diff

```sh
docker images spring-api
# REPOSITORY   TAG        IMAGE ID       CREATED         SIZE
# spring-api   multiple   dc558028e0d0   2 minutes ago   411MB
# spring-api   single     c59a6fdadced   4 minutes ago   897MB
```
